50abbb297394739ec9d85917f8c32aa8bcfa0bfe.query:
select
            state
        from cfd_states
        where cfd_id = ?
        order by id desc
        limit 1;

63c8fd1a1512b55c19feea463dbb6a0fdf98a325.query:
select
            orders.uuid as order_id,
            orders.initial_price as price,
            orders.min_quantity as min_quantity,
            orders.max_quantity as max_quantity,
            orders.leverage as leverage,
            orders.trading_pair as trading_pair,
            orders.position as position,
            orders.origin as origin,
            orders.liquidation_price as liquidation_price,
            orders.creation_timestamp as creation_timestamp,
            orders.term as term,
            orders.oracle_event_id,
            cfds.quantity_usd as quantity_usd,
            cfd_states.state as state
        from cfds as cfds
        inner join orders as orders on cfds.order_id = orders.id
        inner join cfd_states as cfd_states on cfd_states.cfd_id = cfds.id
        where cfd_states.state in (
            select
              state
              from cfd_states
            where cfd_id = cfds.id
            order by id desc
            limit 1
        )

8e7571250da58b12f5884f17656e5966957c7798.query:
select
            id
        from cfds
        where order_uuid = ?;

a59cf0824b5e4191c94c229086ce464d1b8084f6.query:
insert into orders (
                uuid,
                trading_pair,
                position,
                initial_price,
                min_quantity,
                max_quantity,
                leverage,
                liquidation_price,
                creation_timestamp,
                term,
                origin,
                oracle_event_id
            ) values (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?);

select
            orders.uuid as order_id,
            orders.initial_price as price,
            orders.min_quantity as min_quantity,
            orders.max_quantity as max_quantity,
            orders.leverage as leverage,
            orders.trading_pair as trading_pair,
            orders.position as position,
            orders.origin as origin,
            orders.liquidation_price as liquidation_price,
            orders.creation_timestamp as creation_timestamp,
            orders.term as term,
            orders.oracle_event_id,
            cfds.quantity_usd as quantity_usd,
            cfd_states.state as state
        from cfds as cfds
        inner join orders as orders on cfds.order_id = orders.id
        inner join cfd_states as cfd_states on cfd_states.cfd_id = cfds.id
        where cfd_states.state in (
            select
              state
              from cfd_states

            order by id desc
